title: Thales Payshield 10K Security Settings
agents: snmp
catalog: hw/Payshield
license: Proprietary
distribution: Proprietary
description:
 This check monitors the security settings of a Thales Payshield HSM via SNMP. It reports PCI compliance, hash security and general settings, LMK status, and a wide range of other security-related parameters as provided by the device.

 The output of the check plugin provides:
 - PCI compliance status
 - Hash security settings
 - Hash general settings
 - Hash configure command
 - Hash audit setting
 - Hash LMK
 - User storage key length
 - PIN length
 - Encrypted PIN length
 - ZMK length
 - Decimalization tables
 - Minimum HMAC length in bytes

 Long output of the check plugin provides:
 - Full security settings table
 - All SNMP security parameters

inventory:
 This check does not create inventory entries.
